{
  "stem": "3973.4",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I remember how many times we were sleeping in bunks, which are four people in a bunk-- four people went to bed at night, and two may be dead the next morning right next to you.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I began to develop the, the already the vestiges of starvation-- you know, puffy cheeks and stomach and thighs.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I have a few days left.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "The-- there were Russians in there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "The bodies were-- they were accumulated so-- I'm talking Russian prisoners.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "But the bodies were accumulated so fast, that they couldn't burn them.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "The crematorium couldn't handle all of the bodies.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And the Russians got worried, so they started cutting out pieces of meat and trading them.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "So the cannibalism started in camp as well.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "Finally, the day before liberation, they called us.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "We had a big gathering.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And the camp commander says that unfortunately, the Americans are approaching.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And they have to turn over the camp to the Americans.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "However, they expect that there will be possibly a battle between the Germans and the Americans.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "So for our safety, they wanted us to go through the tunnels that we have built until the war is over.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "Well, we refused.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "At that point, they couldn't force us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "I mean, most of the Germans were gone, and the guards-- we said no.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And that night, the, the tunnels blew up.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "In some cases, some of camp's people actually did die in that way.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "Anyway, by that time, I was already sort of losing consciousness.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "I didn't know what was going on.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "The next day, the Americans came.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "I was lying there in the bunk.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "I no longer had any feeling for that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I mean, this-- I was too, too far gone.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the fact the Americans came didn't make an impression.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
